title: Scott Eizember Autopsy Report (Department of Corrections)

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Oklahoma Open Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

Scott Eizember's autopsy report, including but not limited to the amount of drugs that were found in his body, a description of his physical state post mortem, cause of death, any and all notes from a post-mortem examination. 

Any and all notes, reports, emails, findings on the execution of Scott Eizember, from the personnel carrying it out, personnel witnessing it and personnel overseeing it. 

Any and all recordings, audio or otherwise from preparation for the execution and during the execution of Scott Eizember.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 business days.

Sincerely,

Gianna Toboni

communications.subject: Nevada Public Records Act Request: LVMPD Files on Scott Dozier
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Nevada Public Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

Any and all files, emails, reports, investigations, police reports, detective's notes on Scott Dozier and his drug dealing, drug manufacturing and drug use between the years 1989 and 2003. Any notes from undercover narcotics operations involving Scott Dozier. The drugs include but are not limited to methamphetamine / meth, Valium and rohypnol. 

Any and all files, detectives' notes, emails, reports on the 1998 explosion that occured at the house Scott Dozier shared with his girlfriend, Kacy Kimball on Cinderella Lane. 

Any and all files regarding adjacent criminal activity by Scott Dozier, including but not limited to fire arms. 

Scott Dozier's aliases include Chadwick Quincy "Chad" Wyatt.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 5 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Gianna Toboni
